  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "DevOps Engineer",
  "description": "<p>We are seeking a DevOps Engineer with strong experience in <strong>CI/CD automation, containerization, cloud environments, and SonarQube</strong> to enhance our delivery efficiency and platform reliability.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Build and maintain <strong>CI/CD pipelines</strong> (Jenkins/GitLab/GitHub/Azure DevOps).</li><li>Manage and deploy containers using <strong>Docker</strong> and <strong>Kubernetes</strong>.</li><li>Implement code quality gates through <strong>SonarQube</strong>.</li><li>Automate infrastructure using <strong>Terraform/Ansible/IaC tools</strong>.</li><li>Monitor environments using Prometheus, Grafana, ELK, or cloud-native tools.</li><li>Collaborate with development and QA to streamline DevOps practices.</li></ul><p><strong>Skills & Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>5+ years in DevOps roles.</li><li>Strong CI/CD automation experience.</li><li>Proficiency in Docker, Kubernetes, and SonarQube.</li><li>Cloud experience -Azure</li><li>Good scripting skills (Bash/Python).</li><li>Knowledge of Git workflows and Linux administration.</li></ul>",
